 being less susceptible to a wide range of diseases from your&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;everyday bacterial and viral infections to more serious conditions like cancer, cardiovascular disease and&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;osteoporosis. We’ve went ahead and compiled the research results for you, so just sit back, pour yourself&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;a cup of green tea and read about some of its many wondrous benefits below that you’re getting with&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;every sip.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;1. Boost immunity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;2. Relieves stress&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;3. Thwart cardiovascular disease.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;4. Guard against Alzheimer’s and Parkinson’s.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;5. Keep asthma in check.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;6. Strengthens bones and teeth.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;7. Lower blood pressure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;8. Fight ovarian cancer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;9.&amp;nbsp; Reduce the risk of colon cancer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;10. Promote longevity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','','','',0),(1416,1,'Diamond Kalkandu, 100g','','','','',0),(1417,1,'Himalaya Gentle Baby Bath, 200ml','','','','',0),(1418,1,'Himalaya Gentle Baby Bath, 100ml','','','','',0),(1419,1,'Colgate Active Salt with lemon Tooth Paste,100g','','','','',0),(1420,1,'Nestea, Iced Tea Lemon Flavour','','','','',0),(1421,1,'Olay Moisturizing Cream, 50g','','','','',0),(1422,1,'Premier Napkin 1 Ply, Special Soft Tissue, 100 pulls','','','','',0),(1423,1,'Premier Special Face Tissue, 100 Pulls - 2 Ply','','','','',0),(1424,1,'Britannia 50- 50 Maska Chaska ','','','','',0),(1425,1,'Johnson Baby Blossom Soap, 75g','','','','',0),(1426,1,'Sunfeast Yippee Noodles Magic Masala - 4 in 1 pack','','','','',0),(1427,1,'Dabur Hommade Coconut Milk, 200 ml','','','','',0),(1428,1,'Holy Mix Aroma Cinnamon + Orange Soap','&lt;p&gt;Our soaps are made out of 100% Coconut oil in the traditional Cold Processing method with the richness of Ayurvedic herbal ext